readable.content: A bearded collie jumps over bars at an agility test course . A black and white dog jumps over a pole . A black and white shaggy dog is jumping over a red and white hurdle . A furry black and white dog jumps over a bar during an agility test . The black and white furry dog jumps over a low pole in a grassy area .
